headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: CORRECTIONS Extreme rainfall has increased 21% since the 1950s in Texas, Oklahoma and Kansas. A U.S. News article on Thursday about intense precipitation incorrectly listed Nebraska as one of those states.
